{"tid":475250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港茶記啲奶茶真係無得輸","createTime":"2017-11-21T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T00:47:34.000Z","uid":71329,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac455a7b470d1aa741b4d536bd2019c781f0f11","tid":475250,"uid":71329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"飲奶茶一定要去茶餐廳飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日見到7仔有得買日本隻透明奶茶，貪得意買黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲一啖就知道中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甜到仆街，茶同奶味好似分開兩樣野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係試過就算<br />\n下次飲奶茶都係要去返茶記飲，凍熱都咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/110845_37d473e6ddd9a12d2adf7c748e2ee2ef.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F110845_37d473e6ddd9a12d2adf7c748e2ee2ef.jpeg&h=eae65e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/110855_ea21c96a2ff967e62b21f7a0e3e38484.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F110855_ea21c96a2ff967e62b21f7a0e3e38484.png&h=dd2c7153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bc1d3ad854d69676013e424b8f42dbf5e1d0082","tid":475250,"uid":48112,"like":24,"dislike":5,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"一定要飲熱 甜度自己控制<br />\n<br />\n天口熱果時焗住飲凍奶茶係差啲"},{"pid":"a8363611ab073d9a1c3a4dccca28285dab9c26a9","tid":475250,"uid":32298,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"奶茶黎講好似一般茶記唔夠大快活沖得好飲..."},{"pid":"7cda06d7d2c6d465ed9a62c9f31f8b294a640b92","tid":475250,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶茶黎講好似一般茶記唔夠大快活沖得好飲...</blockquote><br />\n大家樂呀?"},{"pid":"30b9f123c459d93c83485c4562f32af972ea6eb9","tid":475250,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9359f19409171735ed45c03ba05bbebf41649615","tid":475250,"uid":10905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲過Teh Terik先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度果D?<br />\n甜撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2b002f8c0772ecbf83efebf303c103c8228898","tid":475250,"uid":43413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"大家飲開邊間好飲?"},{"pid":"7a4ebfb95b43c7455b1b45f1d0e704727a825052","tid":475250,"uid":71329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要飲熱 甜度自己控制<br />\n<br />\n天口熱果時焗住飲凍奶茶係差啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但熱起上黎 飲杯凍奶茶都好正喎 最多叫少甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c346acfc300d62738e28430a3e32ce62408bdc8","tid":475250,"uid":73454,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"國內茶餐廳奶茶，泰國奶茶，英式奶茶，台灣奶茶<br />\n<br />\n根本係唔同類別既飲品，只係大家都叫奶茶"},{"pid":"67a2ac5a120d7bee0a400fa13c5faf2169bb8641","tid":475250,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"好彩我唔係飲開奶茶<br />\n淨係飲檸茶同檸水"},{"pid":"f330d830685ad1e52c20720ed27ee89665036489","tid":475250,"uid":146467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"我係用屋企紅茶茶葉加淡奶（好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n茶記既都好似係咁沖"},{"pid":"4d6aaad843289d61c684692ae83ba3c03755eeb5","tid":475250,"uid":129521,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"熱既話一定唔落糖 香好多"},{"pid":"9672d28b0e1e74e88908e3ecc3509300bc7a65f1","tid":475250,"uid":58002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且仲要飲熱<br />\nd奶香同茶味正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6e195a5f913d776c017ff1c7762de8cc9830da","tid":475250,"uid":1052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"鍾意飲茶走"},{"pid":"af403b0c3acf9a8a35beff98c43bcd5e25ad4c94","tid":475250,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意飲茶走</blockquote><br />\n茶走一定會叫少甜<br />\n通常d都係鳩落<br />\n搞到奶味太多又太甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77455b0ef8e1018036c0f9a63d33818cec81552c","tid":475250,"uid":10905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係用屋企紅茶茶葉加淡奶（好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n茶記既都好似係咁沖</blockquote><br />\n唔只啦你估咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾隻茶葉溝埋再拉拉拉拉"},{"pid":"bfc86cdfc7f9581c5e2b338df05e397475f12f8f","tid":475250,"uid":20815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶茶黎講好似一般茶記唔夠大快活沖得好飲...</blockquote><br />\n呢個啱一半，茶記整得好飲果陣係最好飲，但問題係keep唔到水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同一間茶記可以好極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快餐店唔差，同無咁大落差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce1bfb4188b5db28f3bb669b3eb6d5b4bb04e03","tid":475250,"uid":134247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奶茶黎講好似一般茶記唔夠大快活沖得好飲...</blockquote><br />\n呢個啱一半，茶記整得好飲果陣係最好飲，但問題係keep唔到水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同一間茶記可以好極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快餐店唔差，同無咁大落差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「茶記整得好飲果陣係最好飲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37367ed962565a345f4674aed0d80f4d0bcaece6","tid":475250,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"最鐘意飲印度奶茶"},{"pid":"eec5cad1dd42fd5227ee27660cfc63db55ecb1eb","tid":475250,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最鐘意飲印度奶茶</blockquote><br />\n緬甸奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f293aeb691157eeb5548209e6e8d4508951a8eeb","tid":475250,"uid":8638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"係台灣讀書好掛住香港奶茶<br />\n試左勁多間自稱香港奶茶 結果都係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差十幾條街"},{"pid":"5719eb5574903a59345d0ad9017ac3638b57e7dd","tid":475250,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係台灣讀書好掛住香港奶茶<br />\n試左勁多間自稱香港奶茶 結果都係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差十幾條街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二度真係飲唔到香港奶茶隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f6be0b8f405e56b72a6625e2c799dbd88103a8","tid":475250,"uid":106348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"最柒一定係強國&quot;港式奶茶&quot; 都唔撚知邊忽港式 紅茶味極重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f03bd1b8caa5fa76f4c6a75bb41dcc0285047a","tid":475250,"uid":1711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最柒一定係強國&quot;港式奶茶&quot; 都唔撚知邊忽港式 紅茶味極重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早兩年去廣州，一開始覺得幾親切，因為佢地都係講廣東話，雖然有別於我地既口音，但整體都ok，直至我地一行人諗住搵野食，發現有間&quot;港式茶餐廳&quot;，呢個exactly就係個名，屌，好多廣州人話入去試港式野，但完全唔撚係嗰回事，連個出前一丁都煮到屎咁，喺嗰到只要加港式兩個字就賣好撚貴，$4x食公仔麵我屌你咩"},{"pid":"fcacb02ae60124fbf5fb81e60956eaeead11f582","tid":475250,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"外地不嬲都食唔到當地口味架啦<br />\n都唔知有咩好嘈<br />\n<br />\n好似係香港食日本拉麵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}